DANCER and author Reabetswe Kungwane,10, has just stepped off a terribly long flight from Hollywood, Florida but doesn’t appear to be tired or suffering from jet lag. Before we proceed with the business of the day, she gives us a glimpse of some dance moves she performed when she participated in an American Dance Awards competition where she bagged two trophies. Kungwane scooped the trophies for her Acro Solo when she took part last week. To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser that
